T1  - Identity Orientations And Forms Of Social Exchange In Organizations
AU  - Flynn, Francis J.
Y1  - 2005/10/01
PY  - 2005
DA  - 2005/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.2005.18378875
DO  - 10.5465/amr.2005.18378875
